channel.title: [PI]Moving-Pkz! Skillcape emotes, easter egg, 100% barrows, Godwars and MORE!
channel.description:
[size=36pt][center]Moving-Pkz official release![/center][/size] [center]Hey guys, well since my PS3 got the YLOD and my development team basically gave up on WaleedScape and I, waleed took some pics of the server and decided that we release it :D NOTE: Joey is my first name so don't say i aint part of this development...[/center]
[b]Server:[/b] http://uppit.com/xa2p7mucmokq/Moving-Pkz_source.rar [b]Client:[/b] http://uppit.com/ubtc9iwbkj2t/Moving-Pkz_client.rar
[size=24pt][center]Features[/center][/size] NOTE: some of this is taken from aintaro's Eudora world cuz i cba to type it all again... -Full Pest control -Pest control Exchange -Full Barrows -Barrows Reward Chest -Ice Cave Miningame -Ice Cave Minigame Exchange -Smoke Dungeon -Kq Entrance -Investement System -Investement Rewards -Faction Rewards -Member Option -Changing Game Option -Hunter (butterfly's) -Hunter Items have correct prices -Full Stall Thieving ! -Full Woodcutting -Full fishing -Silverlight 100 charges special ! -Dragon Claws correct Interface -Dragon Claws Special On players and NPC -Fully Working Clan Chat -All Dupes Fixed -X Logging Fixed -Following Disabled ( no more running through wallz) -Pvp System added -Pvp Drops added -Pvp interface added -Kbd Correct Attack and hits ! -Red Dragons added -Mage pray protects from dragon breaths now -Npc emotes and gfx all perfect -essence Mining -Perfect runecrafting -Abby Runecrafting -Multiple Runecrafting runes adjusted ! -Construction Interface added alpha -Perfect Rushing -MultiBarrage on players added -Switching Gamesframes -Fully dueling -Full tzhaar fight pits -New food added -Purple sweets added -Crossbow added -Skillcapes Bugs Fixed ! -No more disonnects ! -Fully working npc and player dialogues! -Bank space added -Dark world added -Larxus lands added -all Skillcapes work -Fullgodwars with drops -Godwars Map !
MY SHIT (lol) Fixed ALL dupes, he didnt fix all like the cheat engine dupe for PI and shop dupes, ect... fixed the slayer skillcape bug, apparently mine was fucked for some reason but it was an easy fix clipped around 30% of godwars map, still more to go in V2 clipped all other areas added STQ 100% anim add KQ (1 form) 2 forms comin hopefully in V2 fixed up chaos ele ALOT made it take off every armour piece and it teles u around the area fixed up Wc a bit, it still needs worked fixed a prayer altar bug as it kept disconnecting me giving an Exception error fixed a slgith bug in icecave minigame added 2 new features in barrows, though theres an antileech added picklocking, banana picking, and god capes in mage bank warriors guild 100%, ill give that tomorrow :D [size=36pt][center]Media[/center][/size] [IMG]http://i820.photobucket.com/albums/zz130/waleedtashtoush/m1.jpg[/img][IMG]http://i820.photobucket.com/albums/zz130/waleedtashtoush/m2.jpg[/img][IMG]http://i820.photobucket.com/albums/zz130/waleedtashtoush/m3.jpg[/img][IMG]http://i820.photobucket.com/albums/zz130/waleedtashtoush/m4.jpg[/img][IMG]http://i820.photobucket.com/albums/zz130/waleedtashtoush/m5.jpg[/img][IMG]http://i820.photobucket.com/albums/zz130/waleedtashtoush/m6.jpg[/img][IMG]http://i820.photobucket.com/albums/zz130/waleedtashtoush/m7.jpg[/img][IMG]http://i820.photobucket.com/albums/zz130/waleedtashtoush/m8.jpg[/img][IMG]http://i820.photobucket.com/albums/zz130/waleedtashtoush/m9.jpg[/img][IMG]http://i820.photobucket.com/albums/zz130/waleedtashtoush/m10.jpg[/img][IMG]http://i820.photobucket.com/albums/zz130/waleedtashtoush/m11.jpg[/img][IMG]http://i820.photobucket.com/albums/zz130/waleedtashtoush/m12.jpg[/img]
[size=24pt][center]Additional Notes:[/center][/size]
The warriors guild will be released with server and client tomorrow, im just putting the server and client up for now so this doesnt get locked.
[size=36pt][center]Credits![/center][/size]
Austin and Aintaro WaleedScape Me
